Modeling
✅ Always use a Star Schema — flat tables kill performance
✅ Keep measure tables separate from data tables
❌ Never use many-to-many relationships unless absolutely necessary
DAX
✅ Always use VAR / RETURN — makes debugging 10x easier
✅ Use COALESCE instead of IF(ISBLANK(x), 0, x)
✅ Prefix helper measures with _ (e.g. [_Delta])
❌ Never use calculated columns where a measure works
❌ Avoid FILTER(ALL(Table), ...) — use specific column filters instead
Power Query
✅ Name every Applied Step clearly
✅ Create a Reference query — never modify the source
✅ Disable Load on staging queries
❌ Never hard-code values — use parameters
Report Design
✅ Add a "Last Refreshed" card to every report page
✅ Use bookmarks for navigation between views
✅ Use dynamic titles that reflect slicer selections
❌ Never use more than 3 colors in a single report
❌ Never put more than 5 visuals on one page
